## Patients sub-view (subView === 'patients')

### Patient list
Map PATIENTS from data.js. Each row:
- Flex row, align center, 12px gap, 10px 0 padding, border-bottom rgba(255,255,255,0.04), cursor pointer
- Left icon: 36px circle, bg rgba(255,255,255,0.04), center shows first letter of sex ("F" or "M"), 12px font
- Middle column:
  - ref (14px, 500 weight, rgba(255,255,255,0.85))
  - age + " · " + sex + " · " + condition (11px muted)
- Right column (margin-left auto, text-align right):
  - Formulation name (look up: `FORMULATIONS.find(f => f.id === p.formulationId)?.name`) — 12px, rgba(255,255,255,0.5)
  - Status badge: recovered → green pill, improved → gold pill, tracking → blue pill (bg rgba(45,75,142,0.15), color #60A5FA)
  - Date (10px muted)
- onClick: `setSelectedPatient(p.id)`

## Patient Timeline (selectedPatient !== null)

Show INSTEAD of current sub-view when selectedPatient is set.

Look up: `const patient = PATIENTS.find(x => x.id === selectedPatient);`
Look up formulation: `const formulation = FORMULATIONS.find(f => f.id === patient.formulationId);`

### Back button
"← Patients" — green, onClick: `setSelectedPatient(null)`

### Header
- patient.ref (serif, 20px)
- patient.age + " · " + patient.sex + " · " + patient.date (12px muted)
- "Prescribed: " + formulation.name (12px, green)

### Timeline
Vertical timeline. Each event in patient.timeline:

Left side: vertical line (2px wide, rgba(255,255,255,0.06)) connecting dots.

Each event:
- Relative layout: dot on the left line, content to the right
- Dot: 12px circle. Color by type: consultation → rgba(255,255,255,0.2), prescribed → green, checkin → blue (#60A5FA), final → #4ADE80
- Day label: "Day {day}" (11px bold, rgba(255,255,255,0.5))
- Type icon: consultation → 📋, prescribed → 💊, checkin → 🗓️, final → ✅
- Description text (13px, rgba(255,255,255,0.6))
- Date (10px muted)
- If event.sideEffect: terra pill "⚠️ {sideEffect}"
- If type === 'final': show a larger outcome badge below the text — green card "Outcome: Recovered" or similar

Simple implementation: map timeline array, each item is a div with left padding (30px), a pseudo-dot (or a small div positioned left), and content right.

```jsx
{patient.timeline.map((event, i) => (
  <div key={i} style={{ display: 'flex', gap: 12, paddingBottom: 16, borderLeft: i < patient.timeline.length - 1 ? '2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06)' : '2px solid transparent', marginLeft: 6, paddingLeft: 20, position: 'relative' }}>
    <div style={{ position: 'absolute', left: -7, top: 0, width: 12, height: 12, borderRadius: '50%', background: /* color by type */ }}/>
    <div>
      <div style={{ fontSize: 11, fontWeight: 600, color: 'rgba(255,255,255,0.5)', marginBottom: 2 }}>Day {event.day} · {event.type === 'consultation' ? '📋' : event.type === 'prescribed' ? '💊' : event.type === 'final' ? '✅' : '🗓️'}</div>
      <div style={{ fontSize: 13, color: 'rgba(255,255,255,0.6)', lineHeight: 1.5 }}>{event.text}</div>
      <div style={{ fontSize: 10, color: 'rgba(255,255,255,0.2)', marginTop: 2 }}>{event.date}</div>
      {event.sideEffect && <span style={{ /* terra pill */ }}>{event.sideEffect}</span>}
    </div>
  </div>
))}
```

